sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuth as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 1: User Accesses Dashboard UI
    Browser->>Router: GET / (HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+)
    Router->>OAuth: Reencrypt (HTTPS/8443, service cert)
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth cookie
    OAuth->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080, localhost)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    Backend-->>OAuth: Static frontend assets
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>Browser: HTML/JS/CSS

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 2: API Request to Kubernetes
    Browser->>Router: POST /api/k8s/... (HTTPS/443)
    Router->>OAuth: Reencrypt (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: REST API call (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer token (user's OAuth token)
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: JSON response (TLS 1.2+)
    Backend-->>OAuth: API response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>Browser: JSON response

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query
    Browser->>Router: GET /api/prometheus (HTTPS/443)
    Router->>OAuth: Reencrypt (HTTPS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>Thanos: PromQL query (HTTPS/9092)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics response (TLS 1.2+)
    Backend-->>Browser: Metrics data (via OAuth + Router)

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 4: WebSocket Watch Events
    Browser->>Router: WSS /wss/k8s/* (HTTPS/443)
    Router->>OAuth: Reencrypt (WSS/8443)
    OAuth->>Backend: WS upgrade<br/>base64url bearer subprotocol
    Backend->>K8sAPI: WSS watch (443/TCP)<br/>base64url bearer subprotocol
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch event stream
    Backend-->>Browser: Real-time k8s events (via WSS)
